    <p>Garden of Life's Dr. Formulated line was developed with David Perlmutter, MD, a board-certified neurologist and gut microbiome researcher. The women's formula delivers the broadest strain diversity on this list — 16 distinct probiotic strains with an emphasis on Lactobacillus species known to support vaginal flora, including <em>L. reuteri</em> and <em>L. fermentum</em>. The critical detail that separates this product from competitors: CFU is guaranteed at expiration, not at manufacture. Probiotic viability decreases over shelf life, so products guaranteeing 10 billion CFU at expiration deliver significantly more live organisms than products guaranteeing the same count only at manufacture. For women who want maximum strain diversity to rebuild a disrupted vaginal microbiome, this is the strongest option available.</p>

